04:30.645 --> 04:32.647
♪ One day at a time ♪

04:34.649 --> 04:37.026
-It's so nice to see you.
-Uh-huh.

04:37.110 --> 04:38.194
What's wrong with Elena?

04:40.947 --> 04:41.781
What?

04:41.864 --> 04:44.909
Nothing. I just wanted
to hang outside of group.

04:44.993 --> 04:46.035
It's been a while since--

04:46.119 --> 04:48.746
The last time you wanted to know
lesbian stuff about Elena.

04:49.789 --> 04:51.332
That's the only reason you call.

04:51.416 --> 04:52.709
Come on, girl. That's not true.

04:54.043 --> 04:56.254
It's fine. What do you want to talk about?

04:57.839 --> 05:00.091
What's up with the bees?
Are they coming back or what?

05:01.801 --> 05:03.553
[chuckles]

05:03.636 --> 05:07.640
Just ask me a question about Elena.
It's fine.

05:07.724 --> 05:09.767
I kind of like being your lesbian Yoda.

05:12.145 --> 05:13.396
I think she's having sex.

05:15.148 --> 05:17.025
[in a robotic voice]
I will need another drink.

05:19.736 --> 05:20.737
I don't know Yoda.

05:23.031 --> 05:24.490
[Schneider clears throat]

05:24.574 --> 05:27.702
So your mom has asked me
to give you a little chat

05:27.785 --> 05:29.996
about irresponsible spending.

05:30.079 --> 05:33.291
Yeah. She said to show me all
the stupid stuff you wasted money on

05:33.374 --> 05:34.834
so that I don't end up like you.

05:36.377 --> 05:38.671
It's a program she calls "Scared Smart".

05:41.299 --> 05:44.886
Yeah, she's really starting to lean on me
as a co-parent.

05:46.554 --> 05:47.597
[Schneider] Take a gander.

05:48.514 --> 05:52.226
Really old comic books,
unopened Star Wars toys,

05:52.310 --> 05:54.520
Shirley Temple's tap shoes.

05:54.604 --> 05:56.064
Why did I think they'd fit?

05:57.607 --> 05:59.233
Who would want all this crap?

06:00.276 --> 06:02.570
Schneider, all this stuff is really cool.

06:03.738 --> 06:04.697
Is it?

06:05.823 --> 06:08.159
Or is it just a symbol of a young man

06:08.242 --> 06:11.037
who tried to use money
to fill the hole in his soul?

06:11.704 --> 06:13.331
It didn't work.

06:14.082 --> 06:16.250
Yeah, but now all of this stuff
is worth tons of money.

06:16.334 --> 06:17.877
Is it? Wait. Is it?

06:22.673 --> 06:25.510
You own the Ghostbusters car?

06:29.138 --> 06:30.056
Yes, I do.

06:31.015 --> 06:32.016
Here's a lesson:

06:32.642 --> 06:35.103
I heard that car was
suddenly going up for auction,

06:35.186 --> 06:38.606
so I had to ditch dinner plans
with my favorite Uncle Gary.

06:38.689 --> 06:41.025
He'd just had a triple bypass.

06:41.109 --> 06:42.860
-Wow.
-Yeah.

06:42.944 --> 06:44.904
He died while I was at that auction.

06:46.531 --> 06:48.991
Turns out, he needed a quadruple bypass.

06:51.119 --> 06:53.329
I will always regret that day.

06:53.413 --> 06:56.624
'Cause you were so selfish, you forgot
family is more important than anything.

06:56.707 --> 06:59.502
No. 'Cause I should have waited
and bid on the Back to the Future car.

06:59.961 --> 07:01.587
That thing travels back in time.

07:01.671 --> 07:03.881
I could've gone back
and not bid on the Ghostbusters car.

07:06.843 --> 07:10.179
Or told Gary to have that fourth bypass,
but whatever, your thing works, too.

07:12.265 --> 07:15.143
See, I know what I would say to Elena
if she were straight.

07:15.226 --> 07:17.937
Use a condom. Take the pill.
Don't have sex.

07:18.020 --> 07:20.648
Well, when you're a lesbian,
it's even simpler.

07:20.731 --> 07:22.733
You don't need a condom,
you don't need the pill,

07:22.817 --> 07:24.777
and the best part, four boobs.

07:28.239 --> 07:29.115
Okay.

07:30.283 --> 07:31.701
I get it. It's great.

07:33.119 --> 07:34.954
But what about STDs?

07:35.037 --> 07:38.166
Safe lesbian sex
is not my area of expertise.

07:38.249 --> 07:39.417
I mean, what do you use?

07:40.001 --> 07:42.587
A dish glove? A swim cap? A thimble?

07:45.631 --> 07:47.508
Do you even have a vagina?

07:48.801 --> 07:51.846
There's hardly any risk physically.
She's gonna be fine.

07:52.430 --> 07:54.640
So what? I'm supposed to be okay
that she's having sex?

07:54.724 --> 07:57.143
I'm a mom. She's my kid.
I can't condone this. No, Ramona.

07:58.728 --> 08:00.605
When did I become the bad guy?

08:00.688 --> 08:02.648
I'm just trying to make you less worried,

08:02.732 --> 08:05.943
and I can assume it's with Syd,
who she's been dating forever?

08:07.695 --> 08:08.905
[exhales deeply]

08:08.988 --> 08:11.616
Elena's 17. She is just way too young.

08:11.699 --> 08:13.075
And how old were you?

08:13.159 --> 08:15.036
Seventeen and a half.

08:17.872 --> 08:19.123
And what did your mom say?

08:19.207 --> 08:21.626
[scoffs]
Are you kidding me?

08:21.709 --> 08:22.877
She doesn't know.

08:27.548 --> 08:28.841
I was sneaky.

08:28.925 --> 08:31.761
I didn't put her through the torture
of thinking about this.

08:31.844 --> 08:34.222
As far as she knows,
I had sex once to make Elena.

08:35.348 --> 08:36.933
And how does she think Alex got here?

08:37.016 --> 08:39.018
She tells people she had him.

08:42.730 --> 08:44.690
If you're gonna be
a sexually active teenager,

08:44.774 --> 08:46.108
you need to do it responsibly

08:46.192 --> 08:47.944
and make sure
your parents never find out.

08:48.945 --> 08:51.322
But now I know,
and I have to have an opinion.

08:51.822 --> 08:55.660
And I don't want to be the mom that's all,
"Sex is dirty. You're gonna go to hell."

08:55.743 --> 08:57.703
But I also don't want to be
the mom that's like,

08:57.787 --> 09:00.331
"Use my bed. I'll get you water,
so you stay hydrated."

09:05.336 --> 09:06.629
Now I have to talk to her.

09:07.505 --> 09:09.173
[cries] I don't want to.

09:11.926 --> 09:14.512
Oh, Papito, how are the shoes?

09:14.595 --> 09:16.138
Great. I sold them.

09:16.847 --> 09:20.476
[dish clangs]

09:20.560 --> 09:22.812
I know, I know, but...

09:23.354 --> 09:26.107
they were already worth twice as much
as what I paid for them.

09:26.190 --> 09:28.484
How could you do such a thing?

09:28.901 --> 09:30.987
I stood in line for hours!

09:31.070 --> 09:33.447
I know, and Dr. Berkowitz
got a busted nose.

09:33.531 --> 09:35.616
Oh, please. That's just a scratch.

09:39.579 --> 09:41.497
Abuelita, I really appreciate
what you did.

09:41.581 --> 09:42.456
Mm-hmm.

09:43.082 --> 09:46.335
So I'm going to use some money
to take you out to dinner.

09:49.297 --> 09:51.882
Aww, Papito.

09:53.426 --> 09:56.345
You do a lot for me,
and it's time I paid you back a little.

09:57.054 --> 09:58.472
And unlike Mami,

09:58.556 --> 10:01.350
I'm gonna let you get an appetizer
and a beverage.

10:01.434 --> 10:03.811
[laughs]

10:05.229 --> 10:07.189
I know that's how they get you.

10:07.940 --> 10:09.191
But they're gonna get us.

10:09.734 --> 10:12.903
You are such a good son... Grandson.

10:18.993 --> 10:20.202
Listen, Mami...

10:20.286 --> 10:21.954
Okay, look, you know why I'm here.

10:22.455 --> 10:23.581
We got to do this.

10:23.664 --> 10:25.833
I don't want to do it either,
but here goes.

10:27.752 --> 10:28.628
I'm your mom.

10:29.754 --> 10:31.714
My first instinct is to protect you.

10:32.506 --> 10:33.591
I mean, if I had it my way,

10:33.674 --> 10:37.219
I'd keep you hidden away from the world
in my mouth like a freaking pelican.

10:37.303 --> 10:40.181
Actually, Finding Nemo
is really misleading. Pelicans--

10:40.264 --> 10:42.600
Okay, I'm halfway through
a very prepared speech.

10:49.815 --> 10:52.943
Even though I sometimes wish
it weren't happening, you're growing up.

11:01.035 --> 11:04.080
The first time I had sex, I was 17.

11:05.331 --> 11:06.791
I thought I was ready,

11:07.541 --> 11:09.585
but I kind of had a freak out after.

11:09.669 --> 11:11.003
It's a roller coaster.

11:12.171 --> 11:13.255
One day, you're fine.

11:14.048 --> 11:15.508
Next day, you have sex.

11:15.925 --> 11:19.553
The day after that, the boy you lost
your virginity to doesn't call you back,

11:19.637 --> 11:22.098
and you're filling the glove compartment
of his Camaro with tuna

11:22.181 --> 11:23.808
so he knows he messed with the wrong girl.

11:25.976 --> 11:28.229
Then you're called "Tunelope"
for the rest of high school.

11:28.312 --> 11:29.397
Worth it? Yes.

11:32.024 --> 11:33.609
Okay, you lost me.

11:35.861 --> 11:38.989
[sighs]
What I mean is that it's very emotional.

11:41.242 --> 11:43.369
And also, check your answering machine

11:43.452 --> 11:46.372
'cause maybe he called you while you were
loading up on Dollar Store tuna.

11:52.420 --> 11:54.338
The point I'm trying to make is that...

11:55.548 --> 11:57.258
sex is not a dirty thing...

11:57.842 --> 11:58.843
that you should hide.

12:00.594 --> 12:03.431
But it's also not something
that you should take lightly.

12:07.893 --> 12:09.895
And I just want to make sure
that you're okay

12:09.979 --> 12:11.647
with what did or didn't happen.

12:15.234 --> 12:16.193
So, are you okay?

12:19.363 --> 12:20.239
Well...

12:27.037 --> 12:27.997
Hey, guys.

12:29.832 --> 12:31.709
Mom, that was a really gendered greeting.

12:34.837 --> 12:36.338
Don't try to distract me from the fact

12:36.422 --> 12:38.632
that this door was closed
when you know it should be open.

12:38.716 --> 12:39.884
Okay, I'm sorry.

12:39.967 --> 12:43.512
Okay, I'm sorry too
about the gendered greeting. Later, dudes.

12:43.596 --> 12:44.889
Oh, caught that one.

12:46.807 --> 12:47.933
Can we go to your house?

12:48.476 --> 12:52.730
I'm homeschooled, and my parents are
holding football tryouts for my brother.

12:59.028 --> 13:00.863
We never get to be alone.

13:01.447 --> 13:05.367
And I love just
making out with you, but...

13:05.451 --> 13:07.203
-Yeah.
-Yeah?

13:07.620 --> 13:12.333
Because I think I'm ready for more...
if you're ready.

13:12.416 --> 13:15.294
I'm definitely ready to do more
than fumble with your bra

13:15.377 --> 13:17.379
whenever your mom isn't checking on us.

13:19.840 --> 13:22.343
Which is only when she's in the bathroom.

13:23.552 --> 13:25.346
Remember when she got food poisoning?

13:26.222 --> 13:27.807
That was so hot.

13:31.185 --> 13:33.270
Okay, so what do we do?

13:33.729 --> 13:34.855
Where can we be alone?

13:36.023 --> 13:38.150
What do they do in teen movies?

13:38.234 --> 13:41.779
I feel like a lot of stuff happens
in parked cars.

13:41.862 --> 13:45.908
Damn. I need to learn how to drive
so we can park.

13:48.994 --> 13:50.162
[Alex clears throat]

13:51.330 --> 13:52.289
Alex, what're you doing?

13:52.373 --> 13:54.917
Mom's in the bathroom,
so she's making me stand here.

13:57.545 --> 13:58.838
Can I ask a favor...

13:58.921 --> 14:01.674
since I spend the afternoon
chaperoning two horny nerds?

14:03.425 --> 14:04.635
Sure, honey, anything.

14:05.219 --> 14:06.929
Can I have tomorrow off
from being grounded?

14:07.012 --> 14:08.848
Aww. No.

14:10.140 --> 14:12.601
You screwed up,
and now you are my prisoner.

14:15.104 --> 14:16.689
Psst! Papito.

14:23.445 --> 14:27.283
Do you, uh, need something
from the outside?

14:33.455 --> 14:35.332
The new Yeezys drop tomorrow.

14:35.416 --> 14:37.126
Jesus is coming back tomorrow?

14:39.336 --> 14:41.881
I just spoke to him.
He didn't tell me anything.

14:48.387 --> 14:50.014
Yeezys are sneakers.

14:50.097 --> 14:51.682
I've been saving up for months now,

14:51.765 --> 14:53.934
and if I'm not in line
at the store tomorrow,

14:54.018 --> 14:54.935
they'll all be gone.

14:55.019 --> 14:57.980
Consider it done.

14:58.063 --> 15:02.276
I will get you those shoes
even if I have to cut off somebody's feet.

15:05.738 --> 15:07.239
You just have to stand in line.

15:07.990 --> 15:10.200
Oh, fine. Suck the fun out of it.

15:11.744 --> 15:12.995
Which reminds me.

15:13.078 --> 15:14.413
I will invite Leslie.

15:16.749 --> 15:17.583
Really?

15:17.666 --> 15:20.419
Okay. Thanks. Now, let me tell you
which sneakers to get.

15:20.502 --> 15:24.757
No need. I will just get the ones
that go best with your church pants.

15:26.133 --> 15:27.009
What? No.

15:27.092 --> 15:28.844
Okay. Then I'll get whatever's on sale.

15:28.928 --> 15:30.262
That's worse.

15:32.723 --> 15:37.061
Abuelita, we need to find a way
for you to get me...

15:37.770 --> 15:38.938
exactly what I want.

15:42.942 --> 15:46.195
Is it working? Can you see
what the phone is pointing at?

15:46.278 --> 15:48.697
Yes! Now please turn it around.

15:55.913 --> 15:57.373
[Elena clears throat]

15:58.707 --> 15:59.625
Hey there.

16:00.668 --> 16:03.128
