16:52.761 --> 16:54.513
Yeah, she's not gonna see it that way.

16:55.723 --> 16:58.017
Not that I was totally listening,

16:58.100 --> 17:01.478
but heads-up on that credit card.
It's just a precaution.

17:01.562 --> 17:02.563
