17:24.960 --> 17:26.503
Ugh! Musicians.

17:30.007 --> 17:32.760
Oh! It's our turn finally.

17:32.843 --> 17:34.845
Nice. Remember, just repeat after me.

17:35.512 --> 17:36.722
Hi. How can I help you?

17:38.515 --> 17:40.434
Hey, bro, how are you living?

17:42.853 --> 17:44.772
Hook me up with what is good.

17:45.397 --> 17:46.356
What do you want?

17:46.440 --> 17:48.776
