17:53.655 --> 17:55.324
All right. Next.

17:55.407 --> 17:57.409
-No, no, no, no.
-No, no, no, no.

18:00.245 --> 18:01.288
You're grounded,

18:01.371 --> 18:04.374
which, you know, means you're not supposed
to be on your phone on the weekends.

18:07.461 --> 18:09.379
Hello. Hello, Alex? Hello?

